{"type": "article", "id": 25712, "title": "可粘式收纳袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-21T06:40:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115059Rg9ZaLkEyXbVroxc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">STITX 是一个三人组成的设计团队，成员都是来自新加坡国立大学工业设计专业的学生。以应对快节奏的生活以及越来越紧张的工作空间，他们设计了这个可粘式收纳袋，让你可以轻松地把常用物品放进不同大小的口袋中。除了口袋之外，还有为 13 和 15 寸笔记本电脑设计的收纳袋，就像电脑保护套那样。你可以在他们的<a href=\"http://indiegogo.com/projects/stitx\">众筹页面</a>了解更多信息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150567sGDnLXpaZJQexyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115057mA8TJIK5f4LSB2dV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150574FpXUL7RdSocKVtT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115058w1mbLTiqcS5d3t79.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65136719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}